lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"SlideDeck Home Page\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Tips & Tricks\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"wordpress theme\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34:\"https://www.slidedeck.com/?p=20141\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:600:\"<p>WordPress has opened up a world of possibilities. The advantages cover not only web developers. It also benefits businesses and individuals who find a need for their website. And who doesn’t need a website nowadays? The tech revolution has brought about this need across different fields. Gone are the days...</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/fully-customizable-wordpress-theme/\">A Fully Customizable WordPress Theme Any Client Would Appreciate</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.slidedeck.com\">Responsive WordPress Slider Plugin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"sonal.magapu@hbwsl.com\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22406:\"<p>WordPress has opened up a world of possibilities. The advantages cover not only web developers. It also benefits businesses and individuals who find a need for their website. And who doesn’t need a website nowadays?</p>\n<p>The tech revolution has brought about this need across different fields. Gone are the days when only large businesses had their site. Today, even professionals who are just starting out find it useful to have a website.</p>\n<p><strong>And it’s WordPress that has made this a possibility.</strong></p>\n<p>For those who are unaware of what WordPress is, it is a website creation tool. Its biggest advantage is the fact that it is extremely user-friendly.</p>\n<p>It is very flexible and versatile. It lets even those with small tech background to customize their website. This makes it a popular choice across all content management systems in existence.</p>\n<h2>The WordPress Influence</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.dealfuel.com\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-20156 size-medium\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/holdingWordPress-580x363.jpeg\" alt=\"Fully Customizable WordPress Theme\" width=\"580\" height=\"363\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/holdingWordPress-580x363.jpeg 580w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/holdingWordPress-768x480.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Just how far has the magic of WordPress gone? Here are a few numbers that can show you just how powerful the platform is:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>WordPress holds 58.9% of the CMS market</li>\n<li>26.9% of all websites online are powered by WordPress</li>\n<li>An average of 24 posts are published per second around the world</li>\n<li>WordPress sites are viewed up to 22.17 billion times per month</li>\n<li>WordPress blogs receive up to 46.6 million comments every month</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://torquemag.io/2016/10/13-surprising-wordpress-statistics-updated-2016/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Statistics from Torque, as of 2016.</a></p>\n<p>See these incredible numbers? It’s no surprise WordPress is considered number one.</p>\n<p>The platform allows full customization, especially design-wise. There are hundreds of themes you can use, depending on what niche you work in.</p>\n<p>Among the many different choices, <a href=\"https://www.dealfuel.com/seller/most-customizable-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">ZPLUS is probably the best</a>. It&#8217;s a fully customizable WordPress theme, no doubt about it.</p>\n<h2>The ZPLUS Advantage</h2>\n<p>ZPLUS is a top pick among the themes available to WordPress users. His fully customizable WordPress theme has quite an impressive list of features.</p>\n<p>What makes ZPLUS a top choice for those still in the process of choosing the perfect theme?</p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\">Visual Composer</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.dealfuel.com/seller/most-customizable-wordpress-theme/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-20143 size-medium\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/creating-a-website-580x383.jpg\" alt=\"Fully Customizable WordPress Theme\" width=\"580\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/creating-a-website-580x383.jpg 580w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/creating-a-website-768x507.jpg 768w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/creating-a-website.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\" /></a></p>\n<p>ZPLUS comes with the Visual Composer, a robust drag-n-drop system. It lets you build your pages in no time. You won’t need any advanced web development know-how here.</p>\n<p>Every element you need is easily available no matter what template you use. With both frontend and backend editing modes, it makes building your website a lot easier.</p>\n<h4>Preloader Options</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.dealfuel.com/seller/most-customizable-wordpress-theme/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-20145 size-medium\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/html5-css3-loaders-08-580x290.jpg\" alt=\"Fully Customizable WordPress Theme\" width=\"580\" height=\"290\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/html5-css3-loaders-08-580x290.jpg 580w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/html5-css3-loaders-08.jpg 650w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Creating an effective website means finding everything your audience sees. This includes the time your page is still loading. That’s what your preloader options are for.</p>\n<p>As a fully customizable WordPress theme, ZPLUS gives you the chance to choose your preloader. Upload an image you want your audience to see while your content is loading. You can also choose a color scheme to be used for it. You can disable the preloader anytime as well.</p>\n<h4>Boxed and Wide Version</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.dealfuel.com/seller/most-customizable-wordpress-theme/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-20146 size-medium\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/sitelayout_option2-580x330.jpg\" alt=\"Fully Customizable WordPress Theme\" width=\"580\" height=\"330\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/sitelayout_option2-580x330.jpg 580w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/sitelayout_option2-768x438.jpg 768w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/sitelayout_option2.jpg 802w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Think about what your needs are and choose between a boxed and a spacious layout. This can be readily determined and switched on your admin panel.</p>\n<p>The moment you choose a design, it will automatically be applied to the entire site. Should you choose the boxed layout, you are also given customization options. You can choose a pattern, a solid color, or an image as your background.</p>\n<h4>Header Features</h4>\n<p>Your header can also dictate the efficiency of your website. This is why ZPLUS allows you to customize your header according to your needs.</p>\n<h4>Mobile Menu Design</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.dealfuel.com/seller/most-customizable-wordpress-theme/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-20147 size-medium\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/mobile-nav-designs-30-580x435.jpg\" alt=\"Fully Customizable WordPress Theme\" width=\"580\" height=\"435\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/mobile-nav-designs-30-580x435.jpg 580w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/mobile-nav-designs-30.jpg 690w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Almost everyone’s on mobile, including a lot of your audiences. It’s a good thing ZPLUS lets you tweak the design of your mobile site’s menu. This gives your mobile audience a more seamless experience.</p>\n<h4>Advanced Admin Panel</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.dealfuel.com/seller/most-customizable-wordpress-theme/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-20148 size-medium\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/sidebar_option2-580x332.jpg\" alt=\"Fully Customizable WordPress Theme\" width=\"580\" height=\"332\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/sidebar_option2-580x332.jpg 580w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/sidebar_option2-768x440.jpg 768w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/sidebar_option2.jpg 802w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\" /></a></p>\n<p>As we said before, ZPLUS is one theme you have to take seriously. The admin panel is proof of this. It gives you the power to make every little change around your site as seamless as possible.</p>\n<p>Manage your sidebars, headers, display styles, dropdowns, footers, and all other elements. Despite the vast number of options, everything is laid out in a simple manner. This makes it easy to understand even for WordPress rookies.</p>\n<h4>Menu Hover Styles</h4>\n<p>Are you using horizontal headers or vertical ones? Regardless of what you have, the menu hover styles available for you to use are varied. This gives you complete control on how you want your menu to appear.</p>\n<h4>Mega Menu</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.dealfuel.com/seller/most-customizable-wordpress-theme/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-20149 size-medium\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/MyThemeShop-WP-Mega-Menu-580x311.jpg\" alt=\"Fully Customizable WordPress Theme\" width=\"580\" height=\"311\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/MyThemeShop-WP-Mega-Menu-580x311.jpg 580w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/MyThemeShop-WP-Mega-Menu.jpg 650w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\" /></a></p>\n<p>The mega menu offers almost everything you need. The mega menu allows you to display an even larger set of menus. You can choose icons that can give you a more visually inspiring design.</p>\n<p>You can also choose how your menu loads. You can get it to slide up, slide down, or just fade into the background. The styling options are also incredible. There are for different color schemes and extensive menus.</p>\n<h4>Vertical Navigation</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.dealfuel.com/seller/most-customizable-wordpress-theme/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-20150 size-medium\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/preview01-580x338.jpg\" alt=\"Fully Customizable WordPress Theme\" width=\"580\" height=\"338\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/preview01-580x338.jpg 580w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/preview01-768x448.jpg 768w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/preview01.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Will vertical navigation make it easier for your audiences to find what they need? Do you want viewers to find it easy to go to your site? ZPLUS makes this possible for you.</p>\n<p>This is available in your header options. It even lets you choose whether to place the navigation on the left or the right. You can also make it a scrollable feature, or a fixed one.</p>\n<h4>Unlimited Sidebars</h4>\n<p>Think the existing sidebars aren’t enough for what you need? Well, the ZPLUS theme allows you to use an unlimited number of sidebars. You can also tweak how these sidebars appear.</p>\n<h4>Page Title Bar</h4>\n<p>Not happy with how your page title bar looks? That’s okay. ZPLUS allows you to customize this through the menu. You can change the background color used, as well as the title bar’s height.</p>\n<p>You can even modify the font size you’re using as well as the way the text is aligned. You can decide how your page title bar will be positioned, too.</p>\n<h4>Unlimited Colors</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.dealfuel.com/seller/most-customizable-wordpress-theme/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-20152 size-medium\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/unlimited_color_option-580x565.jpg\" alt=\"Fully Customizable WordPress Theme\" width=\"580\" height=\"565\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/unlimited_color_option-580x565.jpg 580w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/unlimited_color_option-768x748.jpg 768w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/unlimited_color_option.jpg 802w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\" /></a></p>\n<p>The colors you use can dictate the overall appeal it will have on your audience. This is especially true if you’re targeting a particular niche. <a href=\"https://www.dealfuel.com/seller/most-customizable-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">The ZPLUS theme lets you use every possible color.</a></p>\n<p>This is possible through its backend color picker. It enables you to change any hue in every part of the entire theme. You can also tweak the opacity of these colors you choose. This makes it even more consistent with the whole design.</p>\n<h4>Translation Ready</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.dealfuel.com/seller/most-customizable-wordpress-theme/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-20153 size-medium\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/language_feature-580x454.jpg\" alt=\"Fully Customizable WordPress Theme\" width=\"580\" height=\"454\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/language_feature-580x454.jpg 580w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/language_feature.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Are you targeting a global audience? Then effective communication won’t be a problem, with the ZPLUS theme being completely translation-ready.</p>\n<p>This means that your audience can easily translate your text depending on the language they are most comfortable with. This allows you to send the right message the right way.</p>\n<h4>Blog Options</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.dealfuel.com/seller/most-customizable-wordpress-theme/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-20154 size-medium\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/wordpress-blog-themes-1-580x372.jpg\" alt=\"Fully Customizable WordPress Theme\" width=\"580\" height=\"372\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/wordpress-blog-themes-1-580x372.jpg 580w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/wordpress-blog-themes-1-768x493.jpg 768w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/wordpress-blog-themes-1.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Everyone knows how important a blog is nowadays, especially for businesses. On a personal scale, more and more people are becoming interested in blogging as well.</p>\n<p>This is why ZPLUS includes a <a href=\"https://www.dealfuel.com/seller/most-customizable-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">wide variety of options for your blog</a>. It allows you to control how your entire blog would look like on your website.</p>\n<p>There are 12 different designs for you to choose from. Each of them is fully customizable to fit your needs.</p>\n<h4>Portfolio Options</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.dealfuel.com/seller/most-customizable-wordpress-theme/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-20151 size-medium\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/portfolio_option2-580x337.jpg\" alt=\"Fully Customizable WordPress Theme\" width=\"580\" height=\"337\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/portfolio_option2-580x337.jpg 580w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/portfolio_option2-768x446.jpg 768w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/portfolio_option2.jpg 808w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Are you using your WordPress site as your portfolio? If this is the case, then the ZPLUS, a fully customizable WordPress theme is perfect for you. You can choose how you want your portfolio to be displayed.</p>\n<p>Your options include grid, masonry and packer layouts. You can even display them carousel style. The Visual Composer also makes it easy to manipulate all other elements of your portfolio.</p>\n<p>You can easily change the background color, border color, font sizes, and a lot more.</p>\n<h4>Slider Revolution</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.dealfuel.com/seller/most-customizable-wordpress-theme/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-20144 size-medium\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/jQuery-layer-slider-plugin-580x304.jpg\" alt=\"Fully Customizable WordPress Theme\" width=\"580\" height=\"304\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/jQuery-layer-slider-plugin-580x304.jpg 580w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/jQuery-layer-slider-plugin.jpg 650w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\" /></a></p>\n<p>This is another proof that ZPLUS is an amazing fully customizable WordPress theme. The Slider Revolution plugin is one ZPLUS feature you can’t afford to let slide.</p>\n<p>It’s the best slider plugin out there. It gives you a broad range of possible effects, transitions, and animations. It makes it possible for you to display your content the most efficient way possible.</p>\n<h4>Form Options</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.dealfuel.com/seller/most-customizable-wordpress-theme/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-20155 size-medium\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/health-insurance-form-580x290.jpg\" alt=\"Fully Customizable WordPress Theme\" width=\"580\" height=\"290\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/health-insurance-form-580x290.jpg 580w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/health-insurance-form-768x384.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Forms are always a must-have in every website. It allows you to make your audiences more involved. It’s a good thing Contact Form 7 is readily available with the ZPLUS. Now, you can enjoy different form styles depending on your need.</p>\n<p>These do not even cover the entire list of features that come with the ZPLUS &#8211; a fully customizable WordPress theme. You have custom widgets, 4K icons, and footer options, too. This shows you that it doesn’t matter what you’re using your WordPress site for.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.dealfuel.com/seller/most-customizable-wordpress-theme/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-20157 size-medium\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/themes_img-1.1-580x243.jpg\" alt=\"Fully Customizable WordPress Theme\" width=\"580\" height=\"243\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/themes_img-1.1-580x243.jpg 580w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/themes_img-1.1-768x322.jpg 768w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/themes_img-1.1.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\" /></a></p>\n<p>The ZPLUS theme offers the most number of opportunities, customization-wise. This means that it doesn’t matter what your target market is, or what field you belong to. Your pages are going to fit right in no matter what.</p>\n<p>With a fully customizable WordPress theme like ZPLUS, you just can’t lose. Pair the great design and the fabulous layout with even more awesome content.</p>\n<p>This will make your WordPress site go places. Explore every possible option the moment you decide to go for the <a href=\"https://www.dealfuel.com/seller/most-customizable-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">ZPLUS theme</a>. Maximize every single part of it. Do this, and you won’t even wonder why this theme has become so popular among different circles.</p>\n<h2>Try out this fully customizable WordPress theme &#8211; ZPLUS now.</h2>\n<p><span style=\"border-radius: 2px; text-indent: 20px; width: auto; padding: 0px 4px 0px 0px; text-align: center; font: bold 11px/20px \'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif; color: #ffffff; background: #bd081c no-repeat scroll 3px 50% / 14px 14px; position: absolute; opacity: 1; z-index: 8675309; display: none; cursor: pointer; top: 886px; left: 20px;\">Save</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"border-radius: 2px; text-indent: 20px; width: auto; padding: 0px 4px 0px 0px; text-align: center; font: bold 11px/20px \'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif; color: #ffffff; background: #bd081c no-repeat scroll 3px 50% / 14px 14px; position: absolute; opacity: 1; z-index: 8675309; display: none; cursor: pointer; top: 4676px; left: 20px;\">Save</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"border-radius: 2px; text-indent: 20px; width: auto; padding: 0px 4px 0px 0px; text-align: center; font: bold 11px/20px \'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif; color: #ffffff; background: #bd081c no-repeat scroll 3px 50% / 14px 14px; position: absolute; opacity: 1; z-index: 8675309; display: none; cursor: pointer; top: 886px; left: 20px;\">Save</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"border-radius: 2px; text-indent: 20px; wid