}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Free themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Paid themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Premium themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"Responsive themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:6;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"slidedeck3\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:7;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Slider\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:8;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:9;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"wordpress themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34:\"https://www.slidedeck.com/?p=19810\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:584:\"<p>Has your business got a virtual identity? Not yet? Then start now. How? It’s simple – a website is all it takes. WordPress makes it even easier to make attractive, easily accessible websites. WordPress is the leading free website creation platform. It is the easiest, flexible, at the same time...</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wordpress-themes-responsive-image-slider/\">25+ WordPress Themes with an Responsive Image Slider</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.slidedeck.com\">Responsive WordPress Slider Plugin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Akshay Bhujbal\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31219:\"<p>Has your business got a virtual identity? Not yet? Then start now.</p>\n<p>How? It’s simple – a website is all it takes. WordPress makes it even easier to make attractive, easily accessible websites. WordPress is the leading free website creation platform. It is the easiest, flexible, at the same time the most powerful tool currently available for blogging as well as website management.</p>\n<p>It’s simple – a website is all it takes. WordPress makes it even easier to make attractive, easily accessible websites. WordPress is the leading free website creation platform. It is the easiest, flexible, at the same time the most powerful tool currently available for blogging as well as website management.</p>\n<h2>Attract a Lot and Retain Them All</h2>\n<p>A website is a mirror of yourself. The better, the clearer, the smoother, the less clumsy it is, the more interesting it becomes. Therefore, the website has to be user-friendly, so as to attract and retain visitors to your website. Apart from the website content and your target audience, a key factor for a winning user-friendly website is the choice of website theme.</p>\n<h2>Choice of Theme</h2>\n<p>WordPress offers a bucketful of themes to choose from. Only a careful choice of the theme will give you a head start in your work. Simpler, all browser friendly, multilingual compatible and plugin friendly themes are some of the options that website creators look for.</p>\n<p>Research shows that humans understand and grasp things quickly by looking at an image or picture as compared to text. This should make the very premise of specifically including a WordPress theme with responsive image slider in your search for the best theme.</p>\n<h2>What does it mean by WordPress Themes with a Responsive Image Slider?</h2>\n<p>It simply means a WordPress theme which allows users to smoothly navigate through multiple images. Images make the most of any website. Have you ever seen a website without any images? Impossible. “An image speaks a thousand words,” need I say anymore. Hence, having images and an image slider is very important.</p>\n<p>Apart from the image slider, there are themes that may also include video slider, social slider, and sliders supporting animations. The only word of caution here would be to look for a responsive image slider that works perfectly well with different screen sizes or instruments.</p>\n<p>After working through several responsive themes and checking how they work on different machines, here, I list 25+ WordPress Themes with a Responsive Image Slider, all fresh and hand-picked for you.</p>\n<h2>Free WordPress themes with a responsive Image slider</h2>\n<p>The Word is “Free.”</p>\n<p>Free always works better for most of us, especially the starters. WordPress offers a huge array of free themes with the image slider to choose from. Here is a list of few of them:-</p>\n<h4>1. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/experon/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Experon – A Classic Business Theme</a></h4>\n<p><img class=\"size-full wp-image-19842 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Experon-–-A-Classic-Business-Theme.jpg\" alt=\"Experon – A Classic Business Theme\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Experon-–-A-Classic-Business-Theme.jpg 600w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Experon-–-A-Classic-Business-Theme-435x580.jpg 435w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>Experon is neat, clean and simple, but appealing design with a responsive image slider. It is a professional theme, perfect for large businesses. It has all the good qualities of a WordPress theme with image slider, the only drawback being its perfectionist look which is suitable only for certain group of businesses</p>\n<h4>2. <a href=\"https://cyberchimps.com/responsive-theme/\" target=\"_blank\">Responsive – Free popular responsive WordPress theme</a></h4>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-19843 size-full\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/responsive_screenshot1.jpg\" alt=\"Responsive - Free WordPress theme with responsive image slider\" width=\"540\" height=\"502\"/></p>\n<p>With over 10,000 active downloads, this is one of the best WordPress themes that you can grab for free. It is fully responsive and looks great across all devices. It comes with 11 widget areas, nine templates, and four custom menus.</p>\n<h4>3. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/bellini/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bellini – The Family Business Theme</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/bellini/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-19840 size-full\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Bellini-–-The-Family-Business-Theme.jpg\" alt=\"Bellini – The Family Business Theme\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Bellini-–-The-Family-Business-Theme.jpg 600w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Bellini-–-The-Family-Business-Theme-435x580.jpg 435w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>I find Bellini the most suited for family or small scale businesses. The full header image slider is very attractive, hence directs user’s attention. The theme looks simple, which is a plus point. Here, as the image slider occupies most of the space, the social slider is secondary.</p>\n<h4>4. <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/superstore/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">SuperStore – Your Online Store</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/superstore/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-19838 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/SuperStore-–-Your-Online-Store.jpg\" alt=\"SuperStore – Your Online Store\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/SuperStore-–-Your-Online-Store.jpg 600w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/SuperStore-–-Your-Online-Store-435x580.jpg 435w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>SuperStore, an e-commerce theme, comes with a responsive image slider. The image slider can accommodate up to 10 images which can be navigated with the help of side arrows. The slider includes a filmstrip view as well, which increase the&nbsp;aesthetic value of the site.</p>\n<h4>5. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/mh-urbanmag/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">MH Urban Mag – Best suited for Lifestyle and Travel</a></h4>\n<p>MH Urban Mag is one of the best themes with image slider suited for travel, blogging, lifestyle, and magazines. The dark background makes user focus only on images and text in white. Again, for this theme, social buttons or video postings are not easily accessible, which is otherwise a must for such a theme.</p>\n<h4>6.<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/spina/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Spina – A multipurpose attractive theme</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/spina/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-19838 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/SuperStore-–-Your-Online-Store.jpg\" alt=\"Spina - A multipurpose attractive theme\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/SuperStore-–-Your-Online-Store.jpg 600w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/SuperStore-–-Your-Online-Store-435x580.jpg 435w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Spina is a multipurpose attractive theme. The big header image slider has sharing buttons which are easy to locate. The only potential issue with this theme is that the slider can have only three images.</p>\n<h4>7. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/agama/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Agama – Most suitable for Photographers, Celebrities</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/agama/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-19836 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Agama-–-Most-suitable-for-Photographers-Celebrities.jpg\" alt=\"Agama – Most suitable for Photographers, Celebrities\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Agama-–-Most-suitable-for-Photographers-Celebrities.jpg 600w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Agama-–-Most-suitable-for-Photographers-Celebrities-435x580.jpg 435w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Agama Pro is the perfect theme for celebrities and photographers to present their portfolio. The theme comes with an interactive image slider. The theme is flexible and extremely customizable, which is an added advantage.</p>\n<h4>8. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/grow/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Grow – Another Business Theme</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/grow/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-19835 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Grow-–-Another-Business-Theme.jpg\" alt=\"Grow – Another Business Theme\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Grow-–-Another-Business-Theme.jpg 600w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Grow-–-Another-Business-Theme-435x580.jpg 435w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Grow is like Experon in many aspects. It is a free version of Grow Pro. The image slider has a tab like fashion. Grow is best suited for large business companies’ websites.</p>\n<h4>9. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/forest/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Forest – Best Performance Delivered</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/forest/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-19834 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Forest-–-Best-Performance-Delivered.jpg\" alt=\"Forest – Best Performance Delivered\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Forest-–-Best-Performance-Delivered.jpg 600w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Forest-–-Best-Performance-Delivered-435x580.jpg 435w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Forest is with an ample space for exhibiting your love for life. In my view, this theme is best suited for freelancers, writers, bloggers, and photographers. The white-blue combination of colors is soothing to eyes as well as comes strongly in projective the header image on the image slider. The minus point is the site is not responsive.</p>\n<h4><a href=\"https://www.mageewp.com/torch-theme.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">10. Torch – Lighting the World</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.mageewp.com/torch-theme.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-19833 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Torch-–-Lighting-the-World.jpg\" alt=\"Torch – Lighting the World\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Torch-–-Lighting-the-World.jpg 600w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Torch-–-Lighting-the-World-435x580.jpg 435w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Torch is simple but an effective theme. The theme is multipurpose and is responsive. It is a lightweight theme and works for business, travel, lifestyle, people, food, sports, and other subjects. Here again, the social buttons are not easily locatable.</p>\n<h2>The Premium Category – The Best Paid Themes with a Responsive Image Slider</h2>\n<p>WordPress Premium is where your search for a perfect website theme ends. It costs, but it is worth it. Here are some amazingly designed paid WordPress themes with a responsive image slider.</p>\n<h4><a href=\"https://catchthemes.com/themes/studio-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. Studio Pro – Best for Creative Mess</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://catchthemes.com/themes/studio-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-19830 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Studio-Pro-–-Best-for-Creative-Mess.jpg\" alt=\"Studio Pro – Best for Creative Mess\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Studio-Pro-–-Best-for-Creative-Mess.jpg 600w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Studio-Pro-–-Best-for-Creative-Mess-435x580.jpg 435w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Creativity doesn’t have bound, nor is the Studio Pro theme. It is for those who think different, eat differently and work differently. It comes with several personalization widgets to make it altogether different. The header image is full-width broad, but the social buttons are not easily discoverable.</p>\n<h4><a href=\"https://catchthemes.com/themes/studio-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. WEBLOG Pro – The Best of the Lot</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://catchthemes.com/themes/studio-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-19832 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/WEBLOG-Pro-–-The-Best-of-the-Lot.jpg\" alt=\"WEBLOG Pro – The Best of the Lot\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/WEBLOG-Pro-–-The-Best-of-the-Lot.jpg 600w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/WEBLOG-Pro-–-The-Best-of-the-Lot-435x580.jpg 435w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WEBLOG Pro is specifically designed for blogging, news, and freelancing. The versatile theme incorporates multiple image sliders and cards with images, which gives it a nice graphical view. The current user response is five star, and there is no doubt about it.</p>\n<h4><a href=\"https://www.acmethemes.com/themes/acmeblog/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. Acme Blog Pro – The Professional Blog Theme</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.acmethemes.com/themes/acmeblog/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-19831 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Acme-Blog-Pro-–-The-Professional-Blog-Theme.jpg\" alt=\"Acme Blog Pro – The Professional Blog Theme\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Acme-Blog-Pro-–-The-Professional-Blog-Theme.jpg 600w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Acme-Blog-Pro-–-The-Professional-Blog-Theme-435x580.jpg 435w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Acme Blog Pro is a special premium theme made for professional bloggers, commercial writers, and photographers. Currently rated the best in the category, for a first-time user the theme may appear somewhat cluttered – a potential flaw which may need to rectify.</p>\n<h4>4. <a href=\"https://themegrill.com/themes/spacious/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Spacious – A Clean Theme Enriched with Images</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://themegrill.com/themes/spacious/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-19829 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Spacious-–-A-Clean-Theme-Enriched-with-Images.png\" alt=\"Spacious – A Clean Theme Enriched with Images\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Spacious-–-A-Clean-Theme-Enriched-with-Images.png 600w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Spacious-–-A-Clean-Theme-Enriched-with-Images-435x580.png 435w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Spacious is a business theme with minimal text and maximum usage of images. The image slider is broad and full width is making the site look spacious on any device.</p>\n<h4>5. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/accelerate/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Accelerate – A Simple but Effective Theme</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/accelerate/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-19828 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Accelerate-A-Simple-but-Effective-Theme.jpg\" alt=\"Accelerate - A Simple but Effective Theme\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Accelerate-A-Simple-but-Effective-Theme.jpg 600w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Accelerate-A-Simple-but-Effective-Theme-435x580.jpg 435w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Accelerate is mainly for small businesses, portfolio, and blogging. The simple, easy to navigate theme comes with an image slider. The theme is highly responsive and works well on any device.</p>\n<h4>6. <a href=\"https://www.cssigniter.com/ignite/themes/oxium/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Oxium – A Theme for Singers and Musicians</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.cssigniter.com/ignite/themes/oxium/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-19827 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Oxium-–-A-Theme-for-Singers-and-Musicians.jpg\" alt=\"Oxium – A Theme for Singers and Musicians\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Oxium-–-A-Theme-for-Singers-and-Musicians.jpg 600w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Oxium-–-A-Theme-for-Singers-and-Musicians-435x580.jpg 435w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Oxium, the WordPress theme with a responsive image slider, is unique in every aspect. This theme although has relatively less space for images, the overall design highlights the image in the center so strongly that there is no turning back from the website.</p>\n<h4>7. <a href=\"https://www.cssigniter.com/ignite/themes/paperbag/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Paperbag – A Well Thought Theme for Lifestyle</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.cssigniter.com/ignite/themes/paperbag/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-19826 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Paperbag-theme.jpg\" alt=\"Paperbag theme\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Paperbag-theme.jpg 600w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Paperbag-theme-435x580.jpg 435w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Paperbag is best suited for bloggers. The theme offers navigation through photo cards, which is highly interactive.</p>\n<h4>8. <a href=\"https://www.cssigniter.com/ignite/themes/technico/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Technico – A Clean Business Theme</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.cssigniter.com/ignite/themes/technico/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-19825 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Technico-theme.jpg\" alt=\"Technico theme\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Technico-theme.jpg 600w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Technico-theme-435x580.jpg 435w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Technico is a clean, easy to navigate and highly responsive WordPress theme with an image slider. The theme incorporates multiple content widgets, making it easy to create your own website without the need of much coding.</p>\n<h4>9. <a href=\"https://www.cssigniter.com/ignite/themes/eclecticon/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Eclection – For Those Who Think High</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.cssigniter.com/ignite/themes/eclecticon/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-19823 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Eclection-–-For-Those-Who-Think-High.jpg\" alt=\"Eclection – For Those Who Think High\" width=\"600\" height=\"292\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Eclection-–-For-Those-Who-Think-High.jpg 600w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Eclection-–-For-Those-Who-Think-High-580x282.jpg 580w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>The theme gives a great first impression. It is most suited for freelancers and artists. The first page attracts one’s attention on specific work as one opens the website.</p>\n<h4>10. <a href=\"https://www.cssigniter.com/ignite/themes/salon/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Salon – A Theme for Hair Stylists and Beauticians</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.cssigniter.com/ignite/themes/salon/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Salon-–-A-Theme-for-Hair-Stylists-and-Beauticians.jpg\" alt=\"Salon – A Theme for Hair Stylists and Beauticians\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\"/></a></p>\n<p>Salon, as the name suggests, is the theme for hair stylists and beauticians. The WordPress theme with image slider offers a unique and appropriate color scheme for displaying beauty products and styles. The theme has a flexible layout and the full-width image slider is no doubt a plus point is your sales increase.</p>\n<h4>11. <a href=\"https://www.cssigniter.com/ignite/themes/oscillator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Oscillator –Video Slider for the Love of Music</a></h4>\n<p>This theme has a unique design in which the header incorporates a video slider – a must for any theme in this category. There is a streaming audio player embedded in the theme, which of course is for the users to experience live music and download it.</p>\n<h4>12. <a href=\"https://www.premiumwp.com/oikia-real-estate-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Oikia – The Real Estate and Tourism Theme</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.premiumwp.com/oikia-real-estate-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-19821 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Oikia-–-The-Real-Estate-and-Tourism-Theme.jpg\" alt=\"Oikia – The Real Estate and Tourism Theme\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Oikia-–-The-Real-Estate-and-Tourism-Theme.jpg 600w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Oikia-–-The-Real-Estate-and-Tourism-Theme-435x580.jpg 435w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>In Oikia, the full-width image slider comes with a box which displays the image annotation which is of great help for users to quickly learn about the essentials of the property or place. Since this theme is meant for real estate and tourism, it has an embedded dynamic map and offers to filter for any particular location – making it easier to zero down the place of your choice.</p>\n<h4>13.<a href=\"https://creativemarket.com/cssigniter/49888-Olympic-Fitness-Health-theme\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Olympic – Fitness and Health Theme</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://creativemarket.com/cssigniter/49888-Olympic-Fitness-Health-theme\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-19820 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Olympic-–-Fitness-and-Health-Theme.jpg\" alt=\"Olympic – Fitness and Health Theme\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Olympic-–-Fitness-and-Health-Theme.jpg 600w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Olympic-–-Fitness-and-Health-Theme-435x580.jpg 435w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Olympic is specifically designed to promote your gyming business. The theme has an interactive image slider and an even calendar plugin to show the latest date wise updates.</p>\n<h4>14. <a href=\"http://HotelMotel – For Your Hoteling Business\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">HotelMotel – For Your Hoteling Business</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"http://HotelMotel – For Your Hoteling Business\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-19819 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/HotelMotel-–-For-Your-Hoteling-Business.jpg\" alt=\"HotelMotel – For Your Hoteling Business\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/HotelMotel-–-For-Your-Hoteling-Business.jpg 600w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/HotelMotel-–-For-Your-Hoteling-Business-435x580.jpg 435w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>HotelMotel is specially designed for advertising and promoting your hoteling business. A very nice layout, a unique color scheme, and image flashcards make this theme a clean and neat theme.</p>\n<h4>15. <a href=\"https://www.cssigniter.com/ignite/themes/businesstwo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Business Two – A Classic Business Theme</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.cssigniter.com/ignite/themes/businesstwo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-19818 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Business-Two-–-A-Classic-Business-Theme.jpg\" alt=\"Business Two – A Classic Business Theme\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Business-Two-–-A-Classic-Business-Theme.jpg 600w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Business-Two-–-A-Classic-Business-Theme-435x580.jpg 435w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Business Two is a classic business theme for the corporate world. The theme has a milder grayish and authentic color scheme with multiple layout options. There is a full-width image slider to display the best of your firm.</p>\n<h4>16. <a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/concept-minimal-wordpress-portfolio-theme/11238221\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Concept – A NextGen Theme</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/concept-minimal-wordpress-portfolio-theme/11238221\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-19815 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Concept-–-A-NextGen-Theme.jpg\" alt=\"Concept – A NextGen Theme\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Concept-–-A-NextGen-Theme.jpg 600w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Concept-–-A-NextGen-Theme-435x580.jpg 435w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Concept is a NextGen responsive theme for your business. The minimal usage of text is compensated by the image slider and information thumbnails.</p>\n<h4>17. <a href=\"http://vpresspoetry.blogspot.in/p/about.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">VPress – For the Love of Videos</a></h4>\n<p>VPress is for videos, comes with a responsive video slider. This theme is best suited for video streaming websites and channels. The video grid view makes it easier to navigate to the video of your choice.</p>\n<h4>18. Screen – Big Wide Display</h4>\n<p><img class=\"size-full wp-image-19814 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Screen-Big-wide-display.jpg\" alt=\"Screen Big wide display\" width=\"600\" height=\"362\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Screen-Big-wide-display.jpg 600w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Screen-Big-wide-display-580x350.jpg 580w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>Screen is actually a screenful of display theme. This is the theme to show the best of your products. The theme is simplistic and minimalistic in text usage.</p>\n<h4>19. <a href=\"http://kopatheme.com/demo/ultra-mag-magazine-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ultra Mag – Magazine Theme</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"http://kopatheme.com/demo/ultra-mag-magazine-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-19813 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Ultra-Mag-–-Magazine-Theme.jpg\" alt=\"Ultra Mag – Magazine Theme\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Ultra-Mag-–-Magazine-Theme.jpg 600w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Ultra-Mag-–-Magazine-Theme-435x580.jpg 435w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>This is easy to read magazine theme with a central image slider. The black and white combination makes reading a pleasant experience. There is a strong social link support which is a must in the news industry.</p>\n<h4>20. <a href=\"http://kopatheme.com/demo/seramag-demo-page/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">SeraMag – Magazine in Your Hand</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"http://kopatheme.com/demo/seramag-demo-page/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-19812 size-full\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/SeraMag-–-Magazine-in-Your-Hand.jpg\" alt=\"SeraMag – Magazine in Your Hand\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/SeraMag-–-Magazine-in-Your-Hand.jpg 600w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/SeraMag-–-Magazine-in-Your-Hand-435x580.jpg 435w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>SeraMag feels like reading an interactive and dynamic magazine on any device. The highly responsive image slider is full width and quickly summarizes the top trending news – the core of magazine industry.</p>\n<p>Have you used any of the themes before on your site? How was your experience? Or is there any specific theme that we missed out on?</p>\n<p>Please let us know in the comments below.</p>\n<br/><br/><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/pricing/?utm_source=feed_ad&utm_medium=banner&utm_campaign=sd_blog\"><img src=\"//s3.amazonaws.com/assets-slidedeck2/wp-content/themes/slidedeck2/images/sd-rss.jpg\" alt=\"Easily create AWESOME WordPress sliders - Get SlideDeck\" style=\"display:block;border:none;\"/></a><p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wordpress-themes-responsive-image-slider/\">25+ WordPress Themes with an Responsive Image Slider</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.slidedeck.com\">Responsive WordPress Slider Plugin</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=LufacB9q5V0:M6bb1byKKfA:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=LufacB9q5V0:M6bb1byKKfA:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?i=LufacB9q5V0:M6bb1byKKfA:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=LufacB9q5V0:M6bb1byKKfA:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?i=LufacB9q5V0:M6bb1byKKfA:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=LufacB9q5V0:M6bb1byKKfA:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=LufacB9q5V0:M6bb1byKKfA:F7zBnMyn0Lo\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?i=LufacB9q5V0:M6bb1byKKfA:F7zBnMyn0Lo\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/Slidedeck/~4/LufacB9q5V0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:72:\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wordpress-themes-responsive-image-slider/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wordpress-themes-responsive-image-slider/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:38:\"How to Create a WordPress Post Slider?\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/Slidedeck/~3/prwoHGycpE0/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wordpress-post-slider/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Sun, 04 Dec 2016 17:00:23 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:7:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"General\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"SlideDeck 3\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Tutorials\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"slidedeck3\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"slider plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:6;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"WordPress post slider\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34:\"https://www.slidedeck.com/?p=18943\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:539:\"<p>Do you want to showcase your WordPress custom posts in the slider of your website? A WordPress post slider will not only improve traffic for your blog posts but will also improve the visitor engagement with your site. While there are plenty of plugins available for WordPress to get the...</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wordpress-post-slider/\">How to Create a WordPress Post Slider?</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.slidedeck.com\">Responsive WordPress Slider Plugin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Nishtha Dosaj\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5061:\"<p>Do you want to showcase your WordPress custom posts in the slider of your website? A WordPress post slider will not only improve traffic for your blog posts but will also improve the visitor engagement with your site.</p>\n<p>While there are plenty of plugins available for WordPress to get the task done, SlideDeck3 lets you create a WordPress post slider quickly and easily. SlideDeck3 allows you to amazingly present and promote your best WordPress content into the slider.&nbsp; In this tutorial, we will show you how to create a <a href=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WordPress slider</a> for your custom posts.</p>\n<h2>Creating a WordPress post slider for your site:-</h2>\n<h4>Step ONE: &#8211; Creating a WordPress Post Slider</h4>\n<p>First,&nbsp;you need to install and activate the <a href=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/\" target=\"_blank\">SlideDeck3</a> Plugin.</p>\n<p>To create a WordPress Post Slider, Go to <strong>SlideDeck » Manage » Create SlideDeck under </strong>Dynamic Source <strong>» Select Your Posts. </strong>Give a name to the slider. Then save your slider as a draft or publish it.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-18948 size-full\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/wordpress-posts.png\" alt=\"Choose content source - WordPress\" width=\"551\" height=\"576\"/></a></p>\n<h4>Step TWO: &#8211; Configure your Posts source</h4>\n<p>In this section, you can determine</p>\n<ul>\n<li>What posts type you want to display, such as posts, pages, product or any other custom post type</li>\n<li><span class=\"tooltipper slidedeck\">Preferred location where an image be pulled from</span></li>\n<li>Order of the posts</li>\n<li><span class=\"tooltipper slidedeck\">Turn on/off custom crafted excerpt for posts (instead of the post content) when available.</span></li>\n<li>Turn on/off filter by Taxonomy</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-18947 size-full\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/wordpress-settings.png\" alt=\"Configure source - SlideDeck3\" width=\"402\" height=\"379\"/></a></p>\n<h4>Step THREE: &#8211; Publish the WordPress Post Slider to Your Website</h4>\n<p>You’re almost done. It’s time to add your slider to a post or page. Select any of these methods to publish your slider.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-18928 size-full\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/publish-methods.png\" alt=\"Publish methods - SlideDeck3\" width=\"466\" height=\"486\"/></a></p>\n<p>Visit the page/post to see your <a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/docs/#your-posts\" target=\"_blank\">WordPress post slider</a>&nbsp;in action.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-18945 size-full\" src=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/preview-wpposts.png\" alt=\"WordPress post slider\" width=\"546\" height=\"364\"/></a></p>\n<p>We hope this tutorial helped you create a WordPress custom post slider for your site. Add it to your site to provide some interesting and fresh content for your audience to engage with.</p>\n<p>If you have any queries or feedback, please let me know in the comments.</p>\n<p>Also, check out how to create a <a href=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/create-woocommerce-product-slider/\" target=\"_blank\">WooCommerce product slider</a>&nbsp;in WordPress.</p>\n<br/><br/><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/pricing/?utm_source=feed_ad&utm_medium=banner&utm_campaign=sd_blog\"><img src=\"//s3.amazonaws.com/assets-slidedeck2/wp-content/themes/slidedeck2/images/sd-rss.jpg\" alt=\"Easily create AWESOME WordPress sliders - Get SlideDeck\" style=\"display:block;border:none;\"/></a><p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/wordpress-post-slider/\">How to Create a WordPress Post Slider?</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.slidedeck.com\">Responsive WordPress Slider Plugin</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=prwoHGycpE0:SVfHZfo8Clo:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=prwoHGycpE0:SVfHZfo8Clo:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?i=prwoHGycpE0:SVfHZfo8Clo:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=prwoHGycpE0:SVfHZfo8Clo:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?i=prwoHGycpE0:SVfHZfo8Clo:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=prwoHGycpE0:SVfHZfo8Clo:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=prwoHGycpE0:SVfHZfo8Clo:F7zBnMyn0Lo\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?i=prwoHGycpE0:SVfHZfo8Clo:F7zBnMyn0Lo\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/Slidedeck/~4/prwoHGycpE0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/Comm